程序包 net.opentsdb.tools

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    ArgValueValidator
    Title: ArgValueValidator Description: Defines a class that can validate a value instance of a declared ConfigMetaType
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    ArgP
    A dead simple command-line argument parser.
    BuildData
    Build data for net.opentsdb.tools
    ConfigArgP
    Title: ConfigArgP Description: Wraps Config and ArgP instances for a consolidated configuration and command line handler
    ConfigArgP.ConfigurationItem
    Title: ConfigurationItem Description: A container class for deserialized configuration items from opentsdb.conf.json.
    ConfigMetaType.BooleanValidator
    Title: BooleanValidator Description: Validator for booleans (true|false)
    ConfigMetaType.BootLoadableClass
    Title: BootLoadableClassValidator Description: A validator for boot time loadable class names
    ConfigMetaType.ClassListValidator
    Title: ClassListValidator Description: Validator for loadable class lists
    ConfigMetaType.ClasspathConfiguredClassList
    Title: BootLoadableClassValidator Description: A validator for a comma separated list of classnames for which a supplementary classpath has been specified in a ConfigMetaType.FILELIST configuration item named the same as this one but with .classpath appended.
    ConfigMetaType.ClassPathValidator
    Title: ClassPathValidator Description: A class path validator and ClassLoader factory Company: Helios Development Group LLC
    ConfigMetaType.DirFileSystemValidator
    Title: DirFileSystemValidator Description: Validator for fully qualified file names where the parent directory must exist but the file is optional
    ConfigMetaType.FileListValidator
    Title: FileListValidator Description: A validator for a list of existing files or accessible URLs
    ConfigMetaType.FileSystemValidator
    Title: FileSystemValidator Description: Validator for files and directories
    ConfigMetaType.IntegerValidator
    Title: IntegerValidator Description: Validator for integers
    ConfigMetaType.ReadWriteModeValidator
    Title: ReadWriteModeValidator Description: Validator for ReadWrite Modes
    ConfigMetaType.StringValidator
    Title: StringValidator Description: Empty validator for generic string values, used when we don't have a decent or practical validation routine
    ConfigMetaType.TimeZoneValidator
    Title: TimeZoneValidator Description: Validates time zone typed configuration items.
    ConfigMetaType.URLOrFileValidator
    Title: URLOrFileValidator Description: Validator for URLs or Files
    GnuplotInstaller
    Title: GnuplotInstaller Description: Installs the gnuplot invocation shell file
    OpenTSDBMain
    Title: Main Description: OpenTSDB fat-jar main entry point
    OpenTSDBMain.HelpProcessor
    Title: HelpProcessor Description: Command line help processor
    OpenTSDBMain.UIContentExporter
    Title: UIContentExporter Description: Exports the queryui content from the jar to the specified directory
    StartupPlugin
    The StartupPlugin allows users to interact with the OpenTSDB configuration as soon as it is completely parsed, just before OpenTSDB begins to use it.
  • 枚举概要 
    枚举 说明
    BuildData.RepoStatus
    Represents the status of the repository at the time of the build.
    ConfigMetaType
    Title: ConfigMetaType Description: Defines the recognized meta types for command line argument values
